RESOURCE.DESCRIPTION: Helio HEC time based query V1.16.25
RESOURCE.INFO: SELECT stereo_hi_sw_transient.HEC_id,stereo_hi_sw_transient.date,stereo_hi_sw_transient.instrument,stereo_hi_sw_transient.v,stereo_hi_sw_transient.v_err,stereo_hi_sw_transient.long_hg,stereo_hi_sw_transient.long_err,stereo_hi_sw_transient.time_start,stereo_hi_sw_transient.time_1au FROM stereo_hi_sw_transient WHERE time_start>='2003-02-01T00:00:00' AND time_start<='2003-02-10T00:00:00' LIMIT 100 OFFSET 0

FIELD.name: date
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Date that event appears in H12 cameras field of view expressed as YYYY-MM-DD.

FIELD.name: long_err
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in longitude from S-E line.

FIELD.name: time_start
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Estimated launch time of event (assuming instant acceleration).

FIELD.name: time_1au
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Predicted time of arrival at 1 AU.
